description: This file declares export API functions for TLS Session Entry objects, including creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions, primarily serving as an interface for TLS session management.

methods.name: TlsCreateSessionEntry
methods.description: Factory function to create a new TLS session entry object.

methods.name: TlsSeoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the TLS Session Entry object.

methods.name: TlsSeoRemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the TLS Session Entry object.

methods.name: TlsSeoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the TLS Session Entry object.

methods.name: TlsSeoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the TLS Session Entry object.
